        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Comprehensive career guidance, position insights, and industry trends to help you make informed decisions about your professional future
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4 mb-12">
          <Button
            variant="primary"
            size="lg"
            href="/wiki/"
            class="shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            Explore Careers
          </Button>

          <Button
            variant="outline"
            size="lg"
            href="/position/"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
